{
  "stem": "23090.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you sort of thanked him by keeping that part between the two of us, because you didn't want it to get to your dad, because if that guy-- if he ever would tell your dad that you're not prepared and you're not studying, the repercussions were much greater at the house than you would with the-- with the tutor.",
      "word_count": 60
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went, as long as I can recall, at least three times a week, four times a week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was like a criteria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would say two, three times a week.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was individually, believe it or not.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Your parents paid for that separately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and when they came to the house, you-- you went in a certain-- in a little room and you learned to sing some of the songs and-- and you had to bear down.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when he came, he was the master and you had to do what-- it was just a very impressive and a very regimentated lesson.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was more-- I was more afraid of him than I was virtually afraid of anything else in those-- at my young age at the time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was the master.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was the thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I'm afraid not.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I just remember-- he could have been a younger man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have been an older man.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he wore payos and-- and a beard, and he had the garb on and-- There was always a donation given when he left, paid by I don't know what fashion or what manner, but it was equivalent to our contributions and our charitable, benevolent ways that we do here, so there it was on a direct basis, that you-- you didn't send a check or you didn't-- you know, you didn't mail anything in.",
      "word_count": 75
    }
  ],
